Acabo de saber eso.

00:03:44.160 --> 00:03:46.000
Jiu,¡qué buenos que os conocéis!

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:47.840
Te encargo a Yunshen.

00:03:48.800 --> 00:03:50.520
Parace que tendrás que
acudir a un octavo médico.

00:03:51.520 --> 00:03:52.280
Me voy.

00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:54.840
No, no.

00:03:56.200 --> 00:03:56.960
Zhu Jiu.

00:04:17.270 --> 00:04:18.000
Hola, Chen Le.

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:18.880
Soy Zhu Jiu.

00:04:19.240 --> 00:04:20.040
